h; when she drew her hand away, her fingers were spotted with red.\x{201c}Leave it alone,\x{201d} said Will, setting down his apple and rising to his feet. \x{201c}You\x{2019}ll find you heal very quickly.\x{201d}Tessa poked at her left incisor with her tongue. It was flat again, an ordinary tooth. \x{201c}I don\x{2019}t understand what makes them come out like that!\x{201d}\x{201c}Hunger,\x{201d} said Jem. \x{201c}Were you thinking about blood?\x{201d}\x{201c}No.\x{201d}\x{201c}Were you thinking about eating me?\x{201d} Will inquired.\x{201c}No!\x{201d}\x{201c}No one would blame you,\x{201d} said Jem. \x{201c}He\x{2019}s very annoying.\x{201d}Tessa sighed. \x{201c}Camille is so difficult. I don\x{2019}t understand the first thing about her, much less being her.\x{201d}Jem looked at her closely. \x{201c}Are you able to touch her thoughts? The way you said you could touch the thoughts of those you transformed into?\x{201d}\x{201c}Not yet. I\x{2019}ve been trying, but all I get are occasional flashes, images. Her thoughts seem very well protected.\x{201d}\x{201c}Well, hopefully you can break through that protection before tomorrow night,\x{201d} said Will. \x{201c}Or I wouldn\x{2019}t say much about our chances.\x{201d}\x{201c}Will,\x{201d} Jem chided. \x{201c}Don\x{2019}t say that.\x{201d}\x{201c}You\x{2019}re right,\x{201d} Will said. \x{201c}I shouldn\x{2019}t underestimate my own skills. Should Tessa make a mess of things, I\x{2019}m sure I\x{2019}ll be able to fight our way through the slavering vampire masses to freedom.\x{201d}Jem\x{2014}as was his habit, Tessa was starting to realize\x{2014}simply ignored this. \x{201c}Perhaps,\x{201d} he said, \x{201c}you can only touch the thoughts of the dead, Tessa? Perhaps most of the objects given to you by the Dark Sisters were taken from people they had murdered.\x{201d}\x{201c}No. I touched Jessamine\x{2019}s thoughts when I Changed into her. So that can\x{2019}t be it, thankfully. What a morbid talent that would be.\